UP SIGNS SAYING "BLUE LIVES

09:16.890 --> 09:17.657
MATTER."

09:17.657 --> 09:18.691
SIMILAR EVENTS WERE HELD IN

09:18.691 --> 09:20.794
OTHER CITIES AROUND THE COUNTRY.

09:20.794 --> 09:22.295
ANOTHER NEW NATIONWIDE POLL

09:22.295 --> 09:23.530
FINDS AMERICANS INCREASINGLY

09:23.530 --> 09:24.631
CONCERNED ABOUT TERRORISM.

09:24.631 --> 09:26.666
ACCORDING TO PEW, 76% OF THE

09:26.666 --> 09:28.301
PEOPLE IT SURVEYED CALL

09:28.301 --> 09:30.737
TERRORISM "A POLICY PRIORITY"

09:30.737 --> 09:31.838
FOR THE PRESIDENT AND THE NEW

09:31.838 --> 09:32.739
CONGRESS.

09:32.739 --> 09:34.407
THAT WAS JUST BARELY AHEAD OF

09:34.407 --> 09:36.376
THE ECONOMY AS THE TOP PRIORITY.

09:36.376 --> 09:37.844
DURING THE PAST TWO YEARS, THERE

09:37.844 --> 09:39.679
HAS ALSO BEEN A BIG INCREASE IN

09:39.679 --> 09:40.547
THE PERCENTAGE OF AMERICANS

09:40.547 --> 09:42.015
NAMING "STRENGTHENING THE

