MILITARY" AS A PRIORITY.

09:55.929 --> 09:57.096
>> Sreenivasan: AND NOW TO OUR

09:57.096 --> 09:58.431
SIGNATURE SEGMENT, OUR ORIGINAL,

09:58.431 --> 09:59.766
IN-DEPTH REPORTS FROM AROUND THE

09:59.766 --> 10:01.234
WORLD ABOUT CRITICAL ISSUES.

10:01.234 --> 10:02.435
TONIGHT, OUR FOCUS IS ON

10:02.435 --> 10:03.903
ASSISTED SUICIDE.

10:03.903 --> 10:05.205
BRITTANY MAYNARD'S DEATH LAST

