NOVEMBER REIGNITED THE DEBATE IN

10:07.073 --> 10:08.908
THIS COUNTRY ABOUT THE PRACTICE.

10:08.908 --> 10:10.477
ADVOCATES REFER TO IT AS DEATH

10:10.477 --> 10:12.212
WITH DIGNITY, BUT IT IS ALLOWED

10:12.212 --> 10:14.180
IN ONLY A FEW STATES AND IS

10:14.180 --> 10:15.682
OPPOSED BY MANY RELIGIOUS

10:15.682 --> 10:17.217
GROUPS, INCLUDING THE U.S.

10:17.217 --> 10:19.152
CONFERENCE OF CATHOLIC BISHOPS.

10:19.152 --> 10:20.887
BUT ASSISTED SUICIDE IS MUCH

10:20.887 --> 10:22.155
MORE WIDESPREAD IN THE

10:22.155 --> 10:23.923
PREDOMINANTLY CATHOLIC NATION OF

10:23.923 --> 10:26.359
BELGIUM, AND THERE IT'S NOT JUST

10:26.359 --> 10:28.461
FOR TERMINALLY ILL PATIENTS.

10:28.461 --> 10:30.296
A WARNING: OUR REPORT FROM

10:30.296 --> 10:31.831
BELGIUM BY THE NEWSHOUR'S MEGAN

10:31.831 --> 10:33.299
THOMPSON CONTAINS IMAGES THAT

10:33.299 --> 10:35.235
SOME MIGHT FIND DIFFICULT TO

10:35.235 --> 10:36.336
WATCH.

10:40.073 --> 10:41.040
>> Reporter: AS SHE OPENS THE

10:41.040 --> 10:43.009
DOOR TO HER HOME, THIS 34-YEAR-

10:43.009 --> 10:44.944
OLD BELGIAN WOMAN KNOWN AS "EVA"

10:44.944 --> 10:46.946
SEEMS AT EASE, BUT ACTUALLY

10:46.946 --> 10:49.349
SHE'S CHRONICALLY DEPRESSED.

10:49.349 --> 10:50.550
MORE THAN ONCE SHE'S TRIED TO

10:50.550 --> 10:52.552
COMMIT SUICIDE, AND NOW SHE'S

10:52.552 --> 10:54.654
ASKING DOCTORS TO HELP HER.

10:54.654 --> 10:57.290
HELP HER DIE BY EUTHANASIA, ALL

10:57.290 --> 10:58.658
OF IT CAPTURED IN A BELGIAN

10:58.658 --> 11:02.662
DOCUMENTARY.

11:02.662 --> 11:04.430
>> (translated): IT MAY SEEM

11:04.430 --> 11:05.932
STRANGE, BUT I AM LOOKING

11:05.932 --> 11:07.567
FORWARD TO THE REST.

11:07.567 --> 11:08.968
THE CHOICE HAS BEEN MADE.

11:08.968 --> 11:10.570
THE DECISION HAS BEEN MADE.

11:10.570 --> 11:12.105
I'M LOOKING FORWARD TO THE REST

11:12.105 --> 11:14.240
I HAVE LONGED FOR, FOR SO LONG.

11:14.240 --> 11:16.075
>> Reporter: IT MAY SOUND

11:16.075 --> 11:17.911
SHOCKING, BUT IN BELGIUM

11:17.911 --> 11:19.579
EUTHANASIA IS QUITE ACCEPTED,

11:19.579 --> 11:21.014
AND IT'S NOT JUST FOR THE

11:21.014 --> 11:22.348
TERMINALLY ILL.

11:22.348 --> 11:23.616
CHRONICALLY DEPRESSED PATIENTS

11:23.616 --> 11:27.620
LIKE EVA CAN REQUEST IT, TOO.

11:27.620 --> 11:29.289
AND SO, ON A DAY AND TIME SHE'S

11:29.289 --> 11:32.058
CHOSEN, EVA SAYS GOODBYE TO HER

11:32.058 --> 11:33.393
FAMILY...

11:41.701 --> 11:42.869
>> (translated): EVA, ARE YOU

11:42.869 --> 11:43.670
READY?

11:43.670 --> 11:44.938
>> (translated): YES, I AM

11:44.938 --> 11:48.241
READY, DOCTOR.

11:48.241 --> 11:49.208
>> Reporter: ...AND THEN LAYS

11:49.208 --> 11:50.810
DOWN ON HER COUCH.

11:52.445 --> 11:53.880
>> (translated): WOULD YOU

11:53.880 --> 11:54.981
LIKE TO SAY SOMETHING TO YOUR

11:54.981 --> 11:57.450
BROTHER AND SISTER-IN-LAW?

11:57.450 --> 11:58.618
>> (translated): BYE.

11:58.618 --> 11:59.886
>> (translated): SLEEP WELL.

11:59.886 --> 12:00.820
>> (translated): THANK YOU.

12:00.820 --> 12:01.921
>> Reporter: THE MAN KNEELING BY

12:01.921 --> 12:03.323
HER SIDE, ABOUT TO GIVE HER THE

12:03.323 --> 12:05.091
LETHAL INJECTION, IS HER DOCTOR

12:05.091 --> 12:07.193
FOR THE PAST TWO YEARS, DR. MARC

12:07.193 --> 12:08.528
VAN HOEY.

12:08.528 --> 12:10.263
DOCTOR, HOW MANY EUTHANASIAS

12:10.263 --> 12:12.999
HAVE YOU PERFORMED YOURSELF?

12:12.999 --> 12:15.201
>> MORE THAN 100 IN 12 YEARS'

12:15.201 --> 12:16.369
TIME, I THINK.

12:16.369 --> 12:17.537
>> Reporter: DR. VAN HOEY IS A

12:17.537 --> 12:18.805
GENERAL PRACTITIONER AND

12:18.805 --> 12:19.906
PRESIDENT OF ONE OF THE LEADING

12:19.906 --> 12:21.641
RIGHT-TO-DIE ORGANIZATIONS IN

12:21.641 --> 12:22.976
BELGIUM.

12:22.976 --> 12:24.210
HE'S HELPED SHAPED THE COUNTRY'S

12:24.210 --> 12:26.446
POLICY TOWARDS EUTHANASIA, WHICH

12:26.446 --> 12:27.947
CAN BE REQUESTED BY PATIENTS WHO

12:27.947 --> 12:30.350
MEET TWO BASIC CONDITIONS: THEY

12:30.350 --> 12:32.018
ARE EXPERIENCING "CONSTANT AND

12:32.018 --> 12:33.620
UNBEARABLE" SUFFERING, EITHER

12:33.620 --> 12:35.355
MENTAL OR PHYSICAL; AND THEIR

12:35.355 --> 12:37.624
CONDITION IS "INCURABLE."

12:37.624 --> 12:39.125
AND THEN, PATIENTS MUST PUT

12:39.125 --> 12:40.827
THEIR REQUEST IN WRITING.

12:40.827 --> 12:41.995
>> ONLY THING YOU HAVE TO WRITE

12:41.995 --> 12:45.765
DOWN IS YOUR NAME, THE DATE AND

12:45.765 --> 12:47.600
"I WANT EUTHANASIA," AND

12:47.600 --> 12:48.735
SIGNATURE.

12:48.735 --> 12:49.936
>> Reporter: IN THE FEW AMERICAN

12:49.936 --> 12:51.104
STATES WITH LAWS ON THE BOOKS

12:51.104 --> 12:52.939
ALLOWING THIS, PATIENTS MUST

12:52.939 --> 12:54.073
TAKE THE LIFE-ENDING DRUGS

12:54.073 --> 12:55.041
THEMSELVES...

12:55.041 --> 12:57.110
>> I WILL DIE UPSTAIRS IN MY

12:57.110 --> 12:58.878
BEDROOM THAT I SHARE WITH MY

12:58.878 --> 12:59.612
HUSBAND.

12:59.612 --> 13:00.380
>> Reporter: ...LIKE TERMINAL

13:00.380 --> 13:02.181
CANCER PATIENT BRITTANY MAYNARD,

13:02.181 --> 13:03.816
WHO RECENTLY WENT TO OREGON TO

13:03.816 --> 13:05.718
END HER LIFE.

13:05.718 --> 13:07.220
BUT IN BELGIUM, IT'S THE DOCTOR

13:07.220 --> 13:08.588
WHO MUST ADMINISTER THE LETHAL

13:08.588 --> 13:11.157
DOSE, USUALLY AN INJECTION.

13:11.157 --> 13:12.859
>> I START WITH SOME... IT'S A

13:12.859 --> 13:15.895
NARCOTIC DRUG IN A HIGHER DOSE,

13:15.895 --> 13:19.599
TO CREATE A DEEP SLEEP.

13:19.599 --> 13:21.267
AND THEN, LATER ON, WE GIVE

13:21.267 --> 13:23.903
BARBITURATE IN A SHOT.

13:23.903 --> 13:25.371
IF YOU USE AN INTRAVENOUS

13:25.371 --> 13:27.874
INJECTION AND YOU DO IT GOOD,

13:27.874 --> 13:30.643
THE PATIENT IS DEAD IN ABOUT ONE

13:30.643 --> 13:31.811
OR TWO MINUTES.

13:31.811 --> 13:32.812
>> Reporter: ONE OR TWO MINUTES?

13:32.812 --> 13:33.046
>> YES.

13:33.046 --> 13:33.946
>> Reporter: SO IT HAPPENS VERY

13:33.946 --> 13:34.580
QUICKLY.

13:34.580 --> 13:36.282
>> YES, YOU HAVE A LIFE-LINE.

13:36.282 --> 13:37.650
YOU SAY, "ARE YOU READY?

13:37.650 --> 13:38.818
YOU WANT TO GO WITH IT?"

13:38.818 --> 13:40.920
TILL THE VERY END, WE ASK DO YOU

13:40.920 --> 13:42.789
WANT TO GO, BECAUSE THERE'S NO

13:42.789 --> 13:43.823
WAY BACK.

13:43.823 --> 13:45.625
THEN WE GIVE THE INJECTION, AND

13:45.625 --> 13:46.759
(WHISTLES) IT'S GONE.

13:46.759 --> 13:47.660
>> Reporter: YOU TALK ABOUT ALL

13:47.660 --> 13:49.262
THIS VERY MATTER-OF-FACTLY.

13:49.262 --> 13:51.364
>> I'M QUITE USED TO TALK ABOUT

13:51.364 --> 13:54.600
ASSISTED DYING AND SO ON.

13:54.600 --> 13:55.702
IT'S PART OF MY JOB.

13:55.702 --> 13:56.703
>> Reporter: THAT'S RIGHT.

13:56.703 --> 13:58.371
IN BELGIUM, IT CAN BE PART OF A

13:58.371 --> 14:00.039
DOCTOR'S JOB TO END A PATIENT'S

14:00.039 --> 14:01.007
LIFE.

14:01.007 --> 14:03.676
IT'S BEEN THE LAW SINCE 2002.

14:03.676 --> 14:05.244
BELGIUM HAS THE MOST LIBERAL

14:05.244 --> 14:07.080
EUTHANASIA LAW IN THE WORLD.

14:07.080 --> 14:08.581
AND EVEN THOUGH THIS COUNTRY IS

14:08.581 --> 14:10.416
PREDOMINANTLY ROMAN CATHOLIC,

14:10.416 --> 14:11.884
SURVEYS SHOW OVERWHELMING

14:11.884 --> 14:13.252
SUPPORT HERE FOR THE RIGHT TO

14:13.252 --> 14:15.822
DIE BY EUTHANASIA.

14:15.822 --> 14:17.223
SINCE THE LAW PASSED, THE NUMBER

14:17.223 --> 14:19.025
OF BELGIANS CHOOSING EUTHANASIA

14:19.025 --> 14:21.027
HAS STEADILY RISEN EACH YEAR,

14:21.027 --> 14:22.962
WITH MORE THAN 1,800 DYING THIS

14:22.962 --> 14:25.064
WAY IN 2013.

14:25.064 --> 14:26.632
THAT'S AN AVERAGE OF ABOUT FIVE

14:26.632 --> 14:27.967
PEOPLE A DAY.

14:27.967 --> 14:30.903
IN 2014, BELGIUM MADE HEADLINES

14:30.903 --> 14:32.572
WHEN IT BECAME THE FIRST COUNTRY

14:32.572 --> 14:33.773
IN THE WORLD TO EXTEND

14:33.773 --> 14:35.575
EUTHANASIA TO TERMINALLY ILL

14:35.575 --> 14:38.311
CHILDREN OF ANY AGE, ALTHOUGH NO

14:38.311 --> 14:40.413
CASES HAVE OCCURRED SO FAR.

14:40.413 --> 14:42.181
SO, IN BELGIUM, IT'S NOT JUST

14:42.181 --> 14:43.382
THE TERMINALLY ILL WHO CAN

14:43.382 --> 14:45.685
REQUEST EUTHANASIA.

14:45.685 --> 14:47.453
PSYCHIATRIC PATIENTS, NOW

14:47.453 --> 14:48.654
CHILDREN.

14:48.654 --> 14:49.856
IS BELGIUM PUSHING THE

14:49.856 --> 14:50.990
BOUNDARIES WHEN IT COMES TO

14:50.990 --> 14:52.058
EUTHANASIA?

14:52.058 --> 14:53.259
>> I DON'T THINK SO.

14:53.259 --> 14:54.594
I DON'T THINK SO.

14:54.594 --> 14:55.628
>> Reporter: GILLES GENICOT IS A

14:55.628 --> 14:57.196
LAWYER AND CO-CHAIRMAN OF THE

14:57.196 --> 14:58.998
EUTHANASIA CONTROL AND

14:58.998 --> 15:00.700
EVALUATION COMMISSION, WHICH

15:00.700 --> 15:01.901
OVERSEES THE PRACTICE IN

15:01.901 --> 15:02.969
BELGIUM.

15:02.969 --> 15:06.439
>> THE LAW HUMANIZES THE DEATHS

15:06.439 --> 15:08.441
OF TERMINALLY ILL PATIENTS, ON

15:08.441 --> 15:09.675
THE ONE HAND; AND ON THE OTHER

15:09.675 --> 15:11.210
HAND, FOR PATIENTS WHO ARE NOT

15:11.210 --> 15:12.612
TERMINALLY ILL BUT WHO ARE

15:12.612 --> 15:14.547
COMPLETELY HOPELESS, THERE IS A

15:14.547 --> 15:17.016
RESPECT TO THE INDIVIDUAL

15:17.016 --> 15:18.251
AUTONOMY.

15:18.251 --> 15:19.952
I THINK IT'S A MAJOR ADVANCE IN

15:19.952 --> 15:23.422
THE WAY SOCIETY, LAW AND

15:23.422 --> 15:25.491
PHILOSOPHY SEE THIS VERY

15:25.491 --> 15:26.626
IMPORTANT ISSUE.

15:26.626 --> 15:27.660
>> Reporter: THE 16-PERSON

15:27.660 --> 15:29.428
EUTHANASIA COMMISSION-- HALF

15:29.428 --> 15:31.197
DOCTORS, HALF LAWYERS-- MEETS

15:31.197 --> 15:33.199
EVERY MONTH IN BRUSSELS.

15:33.199 --> 15:34.934
BY LAW, AFTER PERFORMING

15:34.934 --> 15:37.203
EUTHANASIA, DOCTORS MUST FILE A

15:37.203 --> 15:38.371
REPORT WITH THE COMMISSION

15:38.371 --> 15:40.606
DETAILING WHAT THEY DID AND WHY.

15:40.606 --> 15:41.841
THE COMMISSION REVIEWS THE

15:41.841 --> 15:43.509
REPORTS TO BE SURE CONDITIONS

15:43.509 --> 15:45.344
SET BY THE LAW WERE MET.

15:45.344 --> 15:47.380
IF NOT, GENICOT SAYS, IN THE

15:47.380 --> 15:49.348
WORST CASE, A DOCTOR COULD FACE

15:49.348 --> 15:51.284
HOMICIDE CHARGES.

15:51.284 --> 15:53.085
THE REPORTS MUST ALSO AFFIRM THE

15:53.085 --> 15:54.887
PATIENT'S REQUEST FOR EUTHANASIA

15:54.887 --> 15:56.923
WAS VOLUNTARY AND THAT TWO

15:56.923 --> 15:58.858
DOCTORS HAD APPROVED IT, THREE

15:58.858 --> 15:59.992
DOCTORS IN THE CASE OF

15:59.992 --> 16:01.828
PSYCHIATRIC PATIENTS.

16:01.828 --> 16:04.163
THESE ARE ALL EUTHANASIA CASES

16:04.163 --> 16:05.331
FROM THE LAST FEW YEARS?

16:05.331 --> 16:06.299
>> YES.

16:06.299 --> 16:07.166
>> Reporter: GENICOT'S OFFICE IS

16:07.166 --> 16:08.935
FILLED WITH REPORTS OF PAST AND

16:08.935 --> 16:09.969
FUTURE CASES...

16:09.969 --> 16:11.470
>> IT'S THE CURRENT BOX.

16:11.470 --> 16:12.205
>> Reporter: ...AND HE SAYS THE

16:12.205 --> 16:13.706
SYSTEM WORKS WELL, GIVING

16:13.706 --> 16:15.575
DOCTORS A PRACTICAL AND HUMANE

16:15.575 --> 16:16.876
WAY TO HELP SUFFERING PATIENTS

16:16.876 --> 16:18.578
DIE PEACEFULLY.

16:18.578 --> 16:20.479
GENICOT SAYS SOME DOCTORS CHOOSE

16:20.479 --> 16:22.048
TO DESCRIBE THAT IN AN OPTIONAL

16:22.048 --> 16:23.783
SECTION OF THE REPORT.

16:23.783 --> 16:25.284
>> VERY, VERY OFTEN, IT'S TO

16:25.284 --> 16:29.188
EXPRESS HOW SERENE, PEACEFUL AND

16:29.188 --> 16:31.290
QUICK THE PROCEDURE WAS; THAT

16:31.290 --> 16:34.126
THE PATIENT WAS GRATEFUL, SAID

16:34.126 --> 16:36.128
THANK YOU TO THE DOCTOR AND WAS

16:36.128 --> 16:37.263
SURROUNDED BY FAMILY AND

16:37.263 --> 16:39.265
FRIENDS.

16:39.265 --> 16:40.132
>> Reporter: BUT IT ISN'T ALWAYS

16:40.132 --> 16:41.167
THAT WAY.

16:41.167 --> 16:42.969
TOM MORTIER'S MOTHER LIEFE HAD A

16:42.969 --> 16:44.737
PASSION FOR TRAVELING THE WORLD

16:44.737 --> 16:46.372
BUT SUFFERED FROM A LIFETIME OF

16:46.372 --> 16:48.140
SEVERE DEPRESSION.

16:48.140 --> 16:50.309
DESPITE 40 YEARS OF THERAPY WITH

16:50.309 --> 16:52.511
SEVERAL PSYCHIATRISTS AND

16:52.511 --> 16:54.380
TREATMENT WITH ANTI-DEPRESSANTS,

16:54.380 --> 16:55.815
SHE CONTINUED TO STRUGGLE WITH

16:55.815 --> 16:57.049
SUICIDAL THOUGHTS AND

16:57.049 --> 16:58.351
HOPELESSNESS.

16:58.351 --> 17:00.586
DEEMED "INCURABLE," SHE WAS

17:00.586 --> 17:02.121
EUTHANIZED IN A HOSPITAL IN

17:02.121 --> 17:04.891
BRUSSELS ON APRIL 19, 2012, THE

17:04.891 --> 17:06.225
DATE MARKED IN HER OWN

17:06.225 --> 17:07.460
CALENDAR.

17:07.460 --> 17:09.028
MOTHER AND SON WERE ESTRANGED AT

17:09.028 --> 17:10.630
THE TIME, AND MORTIER DIDN'T

17:10.630 --> 17:12.098
FIND OUT ABOUT IT UNTIL THE NEXT

17:12.098 --> 17:14.033
DAY WHEN THE HOSPITAL CALLED HIS

17:14.033 --> 17:15.868
HOME WITH THE NEWS.

17:15.868 --> 17:17.470
>> YEAH, IT WAS COMPLETE SHOCK.

17:17.470 --> 17:18.671
OF COURSE, I KNEW THAT MY MOTHER

17:18.671 --> 17:23.276
WAS SUFFERING MENTALLY, BUT SHE

17:23.276 --> 17:24.410
WOULD NEVER HAVE DONE IT

17:24.410 --> 17:25.278
HERSELF.

17:25.278 --> 17:26.412
SHE NEVER WOULD HAVE COMMITTED

17:26.412 --> 17:27.513
SUICIDE.

17:27.513 --> 17:28.414
I WENT TO TALK WITH THE

17:28.414 --> 17:30.283
PHYSICIAN WHO KILLED MY MOTHER,

17:30.283 --> 17:32.585
AND HE TOLD ME THAT HE WAS

17:32.585 --> 17:35.021
ABSOLUTELY CERTAIN THAT MY

17:35.021 --> 17:36.088
MOTHER DIDN'T WANT TO LIVE

17:36.088 --> 17:37.290
ANYMORE.

17:37.290 --> 17:38.858
AND I TOLD HIM, "HOW CAN YOU BE

17:38.858 --> 17:39.892
ABSOLUTELY CERTAIN?"

17:39.892 --> 17:41.594
>> Reporter: WHEN YOU SAID, "WHY

17:41.594 --> 17:43.496
WASN'T I CONSULTED, WHY WASN'T I

17:43.496 --> 17:44.630
INVOLVED?," WHAT WAS HIS

17:44.630 --> 17:46.132
RESPONSE TO THAT?

17:46.132 --> 17:48.100
>> HE SAID THAT MY MOTHER DIDN'T

17:48.100 --> 17:50.603
WANT THE CHILDREN TO BE

17:50.603 --> 17:53.806
CONTACTED, AND HE HAD TO FULFILL

17:53.806 --> 17:56.275
THE WISH OF THE PATIENT.

17:56.275 --> 17:59.812
"THE PSYCHIC SUFFERING HAS BEEN

17:59.812 --> 18:02.448
TOO MUCH, AND I CAN'T GO ON."

18:02.448 --> 18:03.616
>> Reporter: LETTERS MORTIER'S

18:03.616 --> 18:05.017
MOTHER LEFT BEHIND DID LITTLE TO

18:05.017 --> 18:06.419
HELP HIM MAKE SENSE OF HOW SHE

18:06.419 --> 18:07.486
DIED.

18:07.486 --> 18:08.888
BUT WASN'T IT HIS MOTHER'S

18:08.888 --> 18:11.524
CHOICE, AND HERS ALONE, TO MAKE?

18:11.524 --> 18:12.758
MORTIER SAYS HIS MOTHER'S

18:12.758 --> 18:14.160
DEPRESSION CAME PARTLY FROM

18:14.160 --> 18:15.127
BEING ESTRANGED FROM HER

18:15.127 --> 18:17.063
CHILDREN, SO HER DOCTORS SHOULD

18:17.063 --> 18:18.431
HAVE REACHED OUT TO HIM.

18:18.431 --> 18:20.599
AND, HE'S CONVINCED HIS MOTHER,

18:20.599 --> 18:21.701
SEVERELY DEPRESSED AND ON

18:21.701 --> 18:23.769
MEDICATION, WAS NOT IN THE RIGHT

18:23.769 --> 18:24.971
STATE OF MIND TO MAKE SUCH A

18:24.971 --> 18:26.305
DECISION.

18:26.305 --> 18:27.940
>> THE OPTION THAT IS BEING

18:27.940 --> 18:29.275
OFFERED TO HER RATHER THAN

18:29.275 --> 18:30.977
TREATMENT IS DEATH.

18:30.977 --> 18:31.877
>> Reporter: ATTORNEY ROBERT

18:31.877 --> 18:33.379
CLARKE WITH THE CHRISTIAN GROUP

18:33.379 --> 18:35.047
ALLIANCE DEFENDING FREEDOM IS

18:35.047 --> 18:36.716
NOW USING TOM MORTIER'S CASE TO

18:36.716 --> 18:38.150
CHALLENGE BELGIUM'S EUTHANASIA

18:38.150 --> 18:39.819
LAW IN THE EUROPEAN COURT OF

18:39.819 --> 18:41.654
HUMAN RIGHTS, ARGUING IT

18:41.654 --> 18:43.456
VIOLATES THE BASIC OBLIGATION OF

18:43.456 --> 18:45.157
THE STATE TO PROTECT THE RIGHT

18:45.157 --> 18:46.592
TO LIFE.

18:46.592 --> 18:48.361
IF THE COURT TAKES THE CASE, AND

18:48.361 --> 18:50.329
IF IT RULES IN MORTIER'S FAVOR--

18:50.329 --> 18:52.231
A BIG IF-- BELGIUM COULD BE

18:52.231 --> 18:54.166
FORCED TO REWRITE ITS LAW.

18:54.166 --> 18:55.368
>> WHAT WE SEE IN BELGIUM IS A

18:55.368 --> 18:56.268
SLIPPERY SLOPE.

